replies.author: Lucky777777
replies.txt_content: Mar 14, 2014 7:45:20 PM buildcraft.core.Version versionCheck警告: Unable to read from remote version authority.Buildcraft的版本错误，意为该版本MOD已损坏，无法读取，所以服务器不断尝试，并未正常开启。把这个MOD从服务端mods/中删除再重启即可

replies.author: xujh
replies.txt_content: 更新插件连接超时，可以忽略。
